	(2,4,'<p>Let us know you are visiting and we will save you a seat and make sure you are welcome. Alive Church is for everyone, and we want to make you feel welcome, no matter what you believe or where you are on your journey.<br><strong>We are so excited to meet you!</strong></p>',1,'2026-03-05 10:33:02',1),
	(3,4,'<p>Let us know you are visiting and we will save you a seat and make sure you are welcome. Alive Church is for everyone, and we want to make you feel welcome, no matter what you believe or where you are on your journey.<br><strong>We are so excited to meet you!</strong></p>',2,'2026-03-05 10:45:57',1),
	(4,16,'<ul class=\"info-list\">\n                <li><strong>Services:</strong> Sundays • 11:00AM with live worship &amp; teaching.</li>\n                <li><strong>Kids:</strong> Secure check-in, age-specific teaching, sensory-friendly spaces.</li>\n                <li><strong>Parking:</strong> Look for the pink \"You Belong Here\" flags and our team will guide you.</li>\n                <li><strong>Dress:</strong> Trainers or ties—come as you are.</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>Need extra assistance? Email <a href=\"mailto:office@alive.me.uk\">office@alive.me.uk</a> and we\'ll make arrangements.</p>',1,'2026-03-05 10:46:52',1),
