	(62,35,'<p>Alive Church began as a prayer meeting above a shop in Norwich. Today, we gather in our building, homes, and online. Everything we do flows from Jesus\' Great Commission and the Acts 2 church—devoted to teaching, fellowship, generosity, and prayer.</p>\n            <p>We champion unity across generations, creativity that communicates the gospel, and audacious generosity for our cities. We believe in empowering the next generation of leaders through coaching, Alive Leadership College, and hands-on ministry.</p>',1,'2026-03-06 15:34:04',1),
	(63,35,'<p>Alive Church began as a prayer meeting above a shop in Norwich. Today, we gather in our building, homes, and online. Everything we do flows from Jesus\' Great Commission and the Acts 2 church—devoted to teaching, fellowship, generosity, and prayer. test test test</p>\n            <p>We champion unity across generations, creativity that communicates the gospel, and audacious generosity for our cities. We believe in empowering the next generation of leaders through coaching, Alive Leadership College, and hands-on ministry.</p>',2,'2026-03-06 15:34:20',1),
	(64,16,'<ul class=\"info-list\">\n                <li><strong>Services:</strong> Sundays • 11:00AM with live worship &amp; teaching.</li>\n                <li><strong>Kids:</strong> Kids go out to their own dedicated teaching programme after the worship. They\'re sure to have fun.</li>\n                <li><strong>Parking:</strong> Parking is available on Arms Street at the Nelson First School Car Park. Look for the Alive Church Parking sign.</li>\n                <li><strong>Dress:</strong> Trainers or ties, come as you are.</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>Need extra assistance? Email <a href=\"mailto:office@alive.me.uk\">office@alive.me.uk</a> and we\'ll make arrangements.</p>',4,'2026-03-06 15:34:54',1),
	(65,19,'Lost?',2,'2026-03-06 15:34:55',1),
	(66,19,'Lost?',3,'2026-03-06 15:34:57',1),
	(67,56,'\n            <h2>About These Studies</h2>\n<p>This tool was created to give us and you an easy way to look through the bible in context, study and understand the important verses that guide our faith. These in-depth Bible studies have been written to help you understand Scripture more deeply. Each study examines the text verse-by-verse, exploring the historical context, original language, and practical application for today.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>Whether you\'re new to Bible study or have been reading Scripture for years, we pray these resources will enrich your understanding and deepen your faith.</b></p>        ',1,'2026-03-06 17:34:00',NULL),
	(68,56,'\n            \n            <h2>About These Studies</h2>\n<p>This tool was created to give us and you an easy way to look through the bible in context, study and understand the important verses that guide our faith. These in-depth Bible studies have been written to help you understand Scripture more deeply. Each study examines the text verse-by-verse, exploring the historical context, original language, and practical application for today.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>Whether you\'re new to Bible study or have been reading Scripture for years, we pray these resources will enrich your understanding and deepen your faith.</b></p><p>Writing a bible study for every chapter of the bible, all 1,189 of them is a lot of work. If you\'d like to get involved and become an author, please <a href=\"/contact-us\">contact us</a> to volunteer.</p>                ',2,'2026-03-06 18:44:27',NULL),
	(69,57,'Bible Study Library',1,'2026-03-06 18:44:32',NULL),
	(70,49,'Latest Message',1,'2026-03-06 18:49:45',NULL),
	(71,56,'\n            \n            \n            <h2>About These Studies</h2>\n<p>This tool was created to give us and you an easy way to look through the bible in context, study and understand the important verses that guide our faith. These in-depth Bible studies have been written to help you understand Scripture more deeply. Each study examines the text verse-by-verse, exploring the historical context, original language, and practical application for today.&nbsp;</p><p><b>Use this tool in conjunction with a bible.</b> We recommend NIV translations for their ease of reading and good accuracy, but there are many other great options!</p>\n<p><b>Whether you\'re new to Bible study or have been reading Scripture for years, we pray these resources will enrich your understanding and deepen your faith.</b></p><p>Writing a bible study for every chapter of the bible, all 1,189 of them is a lot of work. If you\'d like to get involved and become an author, please <a href=\"/contact-us\">contact us</a> to volunteer.</p>                        ',3,'2026-03-06 22:46:30',NULL),
	(72,56,'\n            \n            \n            \n            <h2>About These Studies</h2>\n<p>This tool was created to give us and you an easy way to look through the bible in context, study and understand the important verses that guide our faith. These in-depth Bible studies have been written to help you understand Scripture more deeply. Each study examines the text verse-by-verse, exploring the historical context, original language, and practical application for today.&nbsp;</p><p><b>Use this tool in conjunction with a bible.</b> We recommend <a href=\"https://www.waterstones.com/book/niv-holy-bible-hodder-classics/new-international-version/9781473697102\">the NIV translation </a>for their ease of reading and good accuracy, but there are many other great options!</p>\n<p><b>Whether you\'re new to Bible study or have been reading Scripture for years, we pray these resources will enrich your understanding and deepen your faith.</b></p><p>Writing a bible study for every chapter of the bible, all 1,189 of them is a lot of work. If you\'d like to get involved and become an author, please <a href=\"/contact-us\">contact us</a> to volunteer.</p>                                ',4,'2026-03-06 22:47:00',NULL),
	(73,56,'\n            \n            \n            \n            <h2>About These Studies</h2>\n<p>This tool was created to give us and you an easy way to look through the bible in context, study and understand the important verses that guide our faith. These in-depth Bible studies have been written to help you understand Scripture more deeply. Each study examines the text verse-by-verse, exploring the historical context, original language, and practical application for today.&nbsp;</p><p><b>Use this tool in conjunction with a bible.</b> We recommend <a href=\"https://www.waterstones.com/book/niv-holy-bible-hodder-classics/new-international-version/9781473697102\">the NIV translation </a>for their ease of reading and good accuracy, but there are many other great options!</p>\n<p><b>Whether you\'re new to Bible study or have been reading Scripture for years, we pray these resources will enrich your understanding and deepen your faith.</b></p><p>Writing a bible study for every chapter of the bible, all 1,189 of them is a lot of work. If you\'d like to get involved and become an author, please <a href=\"/contact-us\">contact us</a> to volunteer.</p>                                ',5,'2026-03-06 22:48:21',NULL),
