	(93,35,'<p>Alive Church began as a prayer meeting above a shop in Norwich. Today, we gather in our building, homes, and online. Everything we do flows from Jesus\' Great Commission and the Acts 2 church—devoted to teaching, fellowship, generosity, and prayer. test test test</p>\n            <p>We champion unity across generations, creativity that communicates the gospel, and audacious generosity for our cities. We believe in empowering the next generation of leaders through coaching, Alive Leadership College, and hands-on ministry.</p>',3,'2026-03-07 16:19:46',NULL),
