	(114,35,'<p class=\"intro-text\">Alive Church was started over 40 years ago as a small group of charismatic Christians in a living room, in a city without a charismatic church. Today, Alive Church is thriving Pentecostal church, a family of all kinds of people doing life together.</p><p>testtestet</p>',14,'2026-03-07 17:07:54',1),
